from sklearn.pipeline import Pipeline
from sklearn.impute import SimpleImputer
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler
from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression

# Pipeline: LogisticRegression with StandardScaler and SimpleImputer
pipe = Pipeline([
    ('imputer', SimpleImputer()),
    ('scaler', StandardScaler()),
    ('classifier', LogisticRegression())
])

# Fit the pipeline with X_train and y_train
pipe.fit(X_train, y_train)

from sklearn.pipeline import Pipeline
from sklearn.impute import SimpleImputer
from sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier

# Pipeline: RandomForestClassifier with MinMaxScaler and SimpleImputer
pipe = Pipeline([
    ('imputer', SimpleImputer()),
    ('scaler', MinMaxScaler()),
    ('classifier', RandomForestClassifier())
])

# Fit the pipeline with X_train and y_train
pipe.fit(X_train, y_train)

from sklearn.pipeline import Pipeline
from sklearn.impute import SimpleImputer
from sklearn.preprocessing import PolynomialFeatures
from sklearn.svm import SVC

# Pipeline: Support Vector Classifier with PolynomialFeatures and SimpleImputer
pipe = Pipeline([
    ('imputer', SimpleImputer()),
    ('poly', PolynomialFeatures()),
    ('classifier', SVC())
])

# Fit the pipeline with X_train and y_train
pipe.fit(X_train, y_train)
